TERP: a Text-mode ERP Client
============================

Usage: terp.py [options]

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -H HOST, --host=HOST  host name
  -P HOST, --port=HOST  port number
  -d DB, --db=DB        database
  -u UID, --uid=UID     user ID
  -p PASSWD, --passwd=PASSWD
                        user password
  --debug               debug mode

